Dr Jasprit ma'am is a kind doctor....and have great concern with children.....I visited physically in hospital only once for my special child......and several times she adviced me on mobile calls as I could not brought my child to hospital.......thank a lot to Jasprit ma'am ..

review: My experience with has been brilliant so far. I do often visit Dr jaspreet for health issue /growth of my kid. Besides, expert in her field, she does possess a human touch especially for kids which distinguish her among all pediatrician I have come across. Very positive and prompt response you will get from her whenever you need any support for her. Thanks & regards Vishal
**** ****** *** give time and explain everything, She also try to give minimum medicine and give best advice for child. Thankyou ...

She is very soft spoken and the way she is explaining about the main reason of disease and remedy is excellent. I have meet her twice for our child treatment,, she is excellent in entire Delhi,, this is my personal experience
